It records her inbound arrival to the United States at Cyril E. King International Airport on December 18, 1999, at 16:26.
She was processed as an alien resident (holder of a U.S. Alien Registration Card) and was 'NOT REFERRED' for secondary inspection.
The record was generated on September 21, 2021, likely in relation to the investigation into her activities.
